Package com.group17.game.core

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Game
    Models a game session for a Profile.
    Graph
    Models the graph structure of a level.
    Leaderboard
    Helper methods to calculate the leaderboards for levels using the profiles completion times.
    LevelReader
    Methods to parse txt level files and build level objects from the data.
    LevelRenderer
    The purpose of this class is to draw out the game itself.
    MessageOfTheDay
    Methods to retrieve the message of the day from the web server.
    Node
    Models a node on a graph.
    Position
    Models a position on the game grid.
    Profile
    Models a profile in the game.
    ProfileManager
    Methods to manage profiles.
